=== AREA ESTIMATE (manual) ===
Based on SKY130 HD typical cell sizes at TT/25C/1.8V:
  $adff  x27  ~  8 um^2 each  =  216 um^2
  $mux   x26  ~  4 um^2 each  =  104 um^2
  $div   x8   ~ 300 um^2 each = 2400 um^2  (dominant)
  $alu   x9   ~ 40 um^2 each  =  360 um^2
  $macc  x9   ~ 50 um^2 each  =  450 um^2
  Other  x10  ~ 4 um^2 each   =   40 um^2
                              -----------
  Total estimate               = 3570 um^2
  (range: 3000--5000 um^2 depending on place-and-route)
